A RESOLUTION
1 Honoring the inspiring journey and achievements of Nolan Sental Smith Jr.; and for other
2 purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Nolan Sental Smith Jr., born on January 18, 2001, in Savannah, Georgia, has
4 shown the world what it means to dream big, work relentlessly, and rise above every
5 challenge in pursuit of greatness; and
6 WHEREAS, from his early days on the football field in youth leagues to his standout
7 performances at IMG Academy and Calvary Day School, Nolan's passion for the game and
8 unwavering determination have been evident in every play he has made, earning him
9 admiration and respect from coaches, teammates, and fans alike; and
10 WHEREAS, Nolan's college career at the University of Georgia was nothing short of
11 remarkable, during which his relentless work ethic, leadership, and dedication as team
12 captain helped the Bulldogs secure back-to-back College Football Playoff National
13 Championships; and
